_:B25411d64b8683ee84648138e4b125524 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The target <code>relatedFeatures</code> for this <code>Connector</code>. This includes all the <code>relatedFeatures</code> other than the <code>sourceFeature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
