_:B648d61a2ec6b2c09970dbb9c0e75fcc5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
_:B648d61a2ec6b2c09970dbb9c0e75fcc5 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#name> "type" .
_:B648d61a2ec6b2c09970dbb9c0e75fcc5 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-many> .
