_:Bdadbca5eb6158eb7edbfd82a0278ef9c <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Bdadbca5eb6158eb7edbfd82a0278ef9c <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "<code>Types</code> that feature this <code>Feature</code>, such that any instance in the domain of the <code>Feature</code> must be classified by all of these <code>Types</code>, including at least all the <code>featuringTypes</code> of its <code>typeFeaturings</code>.  If the <code>Feature</code> is chained, then the <code>featuringTypes</code> of the first <code>Feature</code> in the chain are also <code>featuringTypes</code> of the chained <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#BooleanExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Bdadbca5eb6158eb7edbfd82a0278ef9c .
