_:Be78924a7fb3d6f5fee59c13adb9d3397 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#BooleanExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Be78924a7fb3d6f5fee59c13adb9d3397 .
