<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#BooleanExpressionShape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A <code>BooleanExpression</code> is a <em><code>Boolean</code></em>-valued <code>Expression</code> whose type is a <code>Predicate</code>. It represents a logical condition resulting from the evaluation of the <code>Predicate</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
