_:Badb57c1555733de2e3c7ac837f9e1a46 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#importedMembership> .
_:Badb57c1555733de2e3c7ac837f9e1a46 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Membership> .
_:Badb57c1555733de2e3c7ac837f9e1a46 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:Badb57c1555733de2e3c7ac837f9e1a46 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
