_:B0e489da9dad0b3b48cf8c37070e849ce <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#unioningType> .
_:B0e489da9dad0b3b48cf8c37070e849ce <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
_:B0e489da9dad0b3b48cf8c37070e849ce <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B0e489da9dad0b3b48cf8c37070e849ce <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
