_:Ba514b0ad6ec47dfa7a2b54d043102814 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Ba514b0ad6ec47dfa7a2b54d043102814 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
