_:B54f99038ce6e527feaec70aff35beedf <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Feature</code> that is accessed by this <code>FeatureChainExpression<code>, which is its first non-<code>parameter</code> <code>member</code>.<p/></code></code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#FeatureChainExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B54f99038ce6e527feaec70aff35beedf .
