_:B4f220a659ebda290b88ac94d2a746d34 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#isModelLevelEvaluable> .
_:B4f220a659ebda290b88ac94d2a746d34 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B4f220a659ebda290b88ac94d2a746d34 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this <code>Expression</code> meets the constraints necessary to be evaluated at <em>model level</em>, that is, using metadata within the model."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#FeatureChainExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B4f220a659ebda290b88ac94d2a746d34 .
