_:B2dcbe140efaefbefa3530eba3d3d97b7 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-many> .
_:B2dcbe140efaefbefa3530eba3d3d97b7 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#parameter> .
