<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#FeatureChainExpressionShape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A <code>FeatureChainExpression</code> is an <code>OperatorExpression</code> whose operator is <code>&quot;.&quot;</code>, which resolves to the <code>Function</code> <em><code>ControlFunctions::'.'</code></em> from the Kernel Functions Library. It evaluates to the result of chaining the <code>result</code> <code>Feature</code> of its single <code>argument</code> <code>Expression</code> with its <code>targetFeature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
