_:B2fa998784518977cf8e9cef6adfa467b <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B2fa998784518977cf8e9cef6adfa467b <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B2fa998784518977cf8e9cef6adfa467b <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B2fa998784518977cf8e9cef6adfa467b <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Feature</code> that is referenced by this <code>FeatureReferenceExpression</code>, which is its first non-<code>parameter</code> <code>member</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#FeatureReferenceExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B2fa998784518977cf8e9cef6adfa467b .
