_:B668412992fabb5bc9f8c9cbe251f7995 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B668412992fabb5bc9f8c9cbe251f7995 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this <code>Function</code> can be used as the <code>function</code> of a model-level evaluable <code>InvocationExpression</code>. Certain <code>Functions</code> from the Kernel Functions Library are considered to have <code>isModelLevelEvaluable = true</code>. For all other <code>Functions</code> it is <code>false</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#FunctionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B668412992fabb5bc9f8c9cbe251f7995 .
