_:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
_:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "<code>Types</code> that feature this <code>Feature</code>, such that any instance in the domain of the <code>Feature</code> must be classified by all of these <code>Types</code>, including at least all the <code>featuringTypes</code> of its <code>typeFeaturings</code>.  If the <code>Feature</code> is chained, then the <code>featuringTypes</code> of the first <code>Feature</code> in the chain are also <code>featuringTypes</code> of the chained <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#IndexExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B13c6dd3064a013d58aab4b316ea81a97 .
