_:Ba3e5afcf4ef04acc3a249e57e62b6dcd <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:Ba3e5afcf4ef04acc3a249e57e62b6dcd <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Ba3e5afcf4ef04acc3a249e57e62b6dcd <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#IndexExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Ba3e5afcf4ef04acc3a249e57e62b6dcd .
_:Bc7c5d3af67e1410df82199fac5c18b76 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
_:Bc7c5d3af67e1410df82199fac5c18b76 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#name> "isModelLevelEvaluable" .
_:Bc7c5d3af67e1410df82199fac5c18b76 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Exactly-one> .
_:Bc7c5d3af67e1410df82199fac5c18b76 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#isModelLevelEvaluable> .
