_:B504f97f2f806fab9a198f8743d69f61d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-many> .
_:B504f97f2f806fab9a198f8743d69f61d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#unioningType> .
_:B504f97f2f806fab9a198f8743d69f61d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
_:B504f97f2f806fab9a198f8743d69f61d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
