_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#name> "featuringType" .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-many> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#featuringType> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "<code>Types</code> that feature this <code>Feature</code>, such that any instance in the domain of the <code>Feature</code> must be classified by all of these <code>Types</code>, including at least all the <code>featuringTypes</code> of its <code>typeFeaturings</code>.  If the <code>Feature</code> is chained, then the <code>featuringTypes</code> of the first <code>Feature</code> in the chain are also <code>featuringTypes</code> of the chained <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#InvariantShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Bfe0421e2bbb4d5fd20085080618368ac .
