<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#InvariantShape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An <code>Invariant</code> is a <code>BooleanExpression</code> that is asserted to have a specific <code><em>Boolean</em></code> result value. If <code>isNegated = false</code>, then the result is asserted to be true. If <code>isNegated = true</code>, then the result is asserted to be false."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
