_:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
_:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "<code>Types</code> that restrict the values of this <code>Feature</code>, such that the values must be instances of all the <code>types</code>. The types of a <code>Feature</code> are derived from its <code>typings</code> and the <code>types</code> of its <code>subsettings</code>. If the <code>Feature</code> is chained, then the <code>types</code> of the last <code>Feature</code> in the chain are also <code>types</code> of the chained <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#InvocationExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B8f73e69d29372e3cee21ac07b7525fa0 .
