<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralBooleanShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B01a3be8079cacb684c93374e59e123d6 .
_:B518938337ec4b18767375847f8e4f8a9 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
