_:Bbee7cdbfc365c2781f671c07ab197981 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralBooleanShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Bbee7cdbfc365c2781f671c07ab197981 .
