_:B8f5e723e24835da67cad11d7b1e93f71 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralRationalShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B8f5e723e24835da67cad11d7b1e93f71 .
_:B79f55fe41c5d7bdcc8f9c2ca8456e67d <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
