_:Bc3aa8442397cb08cdd1428f21dbf793f <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:Bc3aa8442397cb08cdd1428f21dbf793f <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Bc3aa8442397cb08cdd1428f21dbf793f <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralRationalShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Bc3aa8442397cb08cdd1428f21dbf793f .
_:Bf7ea151dc42dcf4d207e1c4e00350549 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
