_:Be62e6b6a500fa7a02a9d35b123d65eac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:Be62e6b6a500fa7a02a9d35b123d65eac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:Be62e6b6a500fa7a02a9d35b123d65eac <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:Be62e6b6a500fa7a02a9d35b123d65eac <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralStringShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Be62e6b6a500fa7a02a9d35b123d65eac .
