_:B694d22348f263216aa4e72abd567f1a9 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#name> "type" .
_:B694d22348f263216aa4e72abd567f1a9 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-many> .
