_:Be8659ce765a92ab44f2e90fd1299480b <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Type</code> that is the <code>owningType</code> of the <code>owningFeatureMembership</code> of this <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralStringShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Be8659ce765a92ab44f2e90fd1299480b .
