_:B0b3826c567465b46608ef0cdce050fe7 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#LiteralStringShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B0b3826c567465b46608ef0cdce050fe7 .
_:B55f8453c074c19c41c8b43008eea1de7 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
