_:B4304f3c2a584d4d3c8a2de8a5364d0df <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Membership> .
_:B4304f3c2a584d4d3c8a2de8a5364d0df <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
