_:Beda52c622de93211f3577d9a83812792 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Type</code> that is the <code>owningType</code> of the <code>owningFeatureMembership</code> of this <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#MetadataAccessExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Beda52c622de93211f3577d9a83812792 .
_:B32bb7fc32c5d0b7d78aa0a566e9bdad5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
