_:B22c18a031d8f55b091aa4cbd9de06744 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B22c18a031d8f55b091aa4cbd9de06744 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
