_:B237a03a3d82ac552a2ff08892df39793 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B237a03a3d82ac552a2ff08892df39793 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B237a03a3d82ac552a2ff08892df39793 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
