_:B31abae7f236317a43373eac8e3b7cf8e <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B31abae7f236317a43373eac8e3b7cf8e <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
