_:B2a460dadbbf35086fc9cde8cfc5c0c7d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B2a460dadbbf35086fc9cde8cfc5c0c7d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B2a460dadbbf35086fc9cde8cfc5c0c7d <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B2a460dadbbf35086fc9cde8cfc5c0c7d <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#MultiplicityShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B2a460dadbbf35086fc9cde8cfc5c0c7d .
_:Bd13b2807c402306502ab948ab4b966ab <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
