_:Be96b3a06636612f055be1f0d40ac4875 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:Be96b3a06636612f055be1f0d40ac4875 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this <code>Expression</code> meets the constraints necessary to be evaluated at <em>model level</em>, that is, using metadata within the model."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#NullExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Be96b3a06636612f055be1f0d40ac4875 .
_:B2e94c7bb244398832db85b317c03fc71 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
