_:B7abf1181a6a27d919a2c7d758b75285c <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Membership> .
_:B7abf1181a6a27d919a2c7d758b75285c <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:B7abf1181a6a27d919a2c7d758b75285c <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
