_:B7abf1181a6a27d919a2c7d758b75285c <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
