_:Bba69c34a1748ebe1a750176b94b84669 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#featuringType> .
_:Bba69c34a1748ebe1a750176b94b84669 <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#Type> .
