_:B5e7973267f5dbcf538e6a180eb412539 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#NullExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B5e7973267f5dbcf538e6a180eb412539 .
_:B7fa2b7f025c1730a6455a9e39f9e25bc <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
