_:Bb7d6b7bc405376826e7374c8f5bb680c <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
_:Bb7d6b7bc405376826e7374c8f5bb680c <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this <code>Expression</code> meets the constraints necessary to be evaluated at <em>model level</em>, that is, using metadata within the model."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#OperatorExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:Bb7d6b7bc405376826e7374c8f5bb680c .
