_:Beea29018f7346d7a042ceb9497fc8f0e <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>parameters</code> of this <code>Step</code>, which are defined as its <code>directedFeatures</code>, whose values are passed into and/or out of a performance of the <code>Step</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
