<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ParameterMembershipShape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A <code>ParameterMembership</code> is a <code>FeatureMembership</code> that identifies its <code>memberFeature</code> as a parameter, which is always owned, and must have a <code>direction</code>. A <code>ParameterMembership</code> must be owned by a <code>Behavior</code>, a <code>Step</code>, or the <code>result</code> parameter of a <code>ConstructorExpression</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ParameterMembershipShape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "ParameterMembershipShape"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
