_:B53960511826ad92c455d7fd700d3e4fb <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this <code>Expression</code> meets the constraints necessary to be evaluated at <em>model level</em>, that is, using metadata within the model."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#SelectExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B53960511826ad92c455d7fd700d3e4fb .
