_:B1d13c823cc6732371a57e95548314e74 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Memberships</code> in this <code>Namespace</code> that result from the <code>ownedImports</code> of this <code>Namespace</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#SelectExpressionShape> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#property> _:B1d13c823cc6732371a57e95548314e74 .
_:B0fdb5be27facf2b015b63c3b9b4d9ee7 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
