_:B463a83d7e6a9682568dac75d512adaab <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
_:B463a83d7e6a9682568dac75d512adaab <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
_:B463a83d7e6a9682568dac75d512adaab <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>Type</code> that is the <code>owningType</code> of the <code>owningFeatureMembership</code> of this <code>Feature</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
