<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedCrossSubsetting> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The one <code>ownedSubsetting</code> of this <code>Feature</code>, if any, that is a <code>CrossSubsetting}, for which the <code>Feature</code> is the <code>crossingFeature</code>.</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureChaining> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
