<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureInverting> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#range> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#FeatureInverting> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureInverting> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureInverting> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureInverting> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#valueType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Resource> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedFeatureInverting> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The <code>ownedRelationships</code> of this <code>Feature</code> that are <code>FeatureInvertings</code> and for which the <code>Feature</code> is the <code>featureInverted</code>."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedRedefinition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
