<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedRedefinition> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#ownedRedefinition> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Either> .
