<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#isLibraryElement> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#isLibraryElement> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Whether this Element is contained in the ownership tree of a library model."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
