<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/20250201/shapes#name> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The name to be used for this <code>Element</code> during name resolution within its <code>owningNamespace</code>. This is derived using the <code>effectiveName()</code> operation. By default, it is the same as the <code>declaredName</code>, but this is overridden for certain kinds of <code>Elements</code> to compute a <code>name</code> even when the <code>declaredName</code> is null."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#XMLLiteral> .
